Install dependencies

Ubuntu / Debian
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install -y tesseract-ocr tesseract-ocr-fra poppler-utils
pip install -U ocrmypdf pandas pyarrow regex tqdm spacy
python -m spacy download fr_core_news_sm


macOS (Homebrew)
brew install tesseract poppler
brew install tesseract-lang  # may be optional depending on your brew setup
pip install -U ocrmypdf pandas pyarrow regex tqdm

Windows
Install Tesseract and add it to PATH
Install poppler (or use a python wheel/conda setup)
Then:
pip install -U ocrmypdf pandas pyarrow regex tqdm

RUN THE CODE

python pdf_ocr_to_sentences_table.py \
  --input_pdf "/mnt/data/La-ballade-de-Pern-intégrale-McCaffrey_-Anne-La-Ballade-de-Pern_-2015-12-21-9782823821758-bc3525592e.pdf" \
  --book_title "La Ballade de Pern — Intégrale (Anne McCaffrey)" \
  --out_dir "./pern_ocr_out" \
  --lang "fra"
  

Outputs:
*.reflowed.txt (sanity-check page-to-text reflow)
*.sentences.csv
*.sentences.parquet
